{"title":"缓解资金紧张八法","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":8,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"缓解资金紧张八法"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一、筹集闲资，散钱整用。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二、引进他资，外钱我用。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三、挖掘滞资，死钱活用。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四、扩大积累，聚钱专用。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五、加速周转，现钱快用。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六、管好资金，防止此钱彼用。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七、优化资金，小钱大用。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八、履行节约，节支俭用。　　（8月14日《中国乡镇企业报》）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}